nonetheless comparing real war to EQ war is rather stupid and pointless imo, i thought/think pino is a nice guy and didnt particularly enjoy deleveling him persay, but he is on the other team, hence an enemy, thus you get no quarter from me, and most of the rest of my guild thinks the same.<br>
